'''喬治·切爾斯頓·史普林格三世'''（{{lang-en|'''George Chelston Springer III'''}}，{{bd|1989年|9月19日|}}），為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[外野手|外野手]]，目前效力於[[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]。先前曾效力於太空人長達7個球季。

[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2011年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，太空人隊在第1輪11順位選進史普林格。他於2014年登上大聯盟，2017年拿下世界大賽冠軍。他在該年的世界大賽擊出5支全壘打，並拿下世界大賽MVP。

史普林格還有波多黎各和巴拿馬的血統。

==職業生涯==
===休士頓太空人===
====2014年====
4月16日，史普林格登上大聯盟。他在該場比賽擊出大聯盟生涯首安，是一支內野安打。5月8日，史普林格擊出大聯盟生涯首轟。6月26日，他擊出單季第15轟，打破了太空人菜鳥在明星賽前的全壘打紀錄。7月23日，他因為股四頭肌緊繃而進入傷兵名單。<ref name=Ortiz>{{cite web|last1=De Jesus Ortiz|first1=Jose|title=George Springer to sit rest of season|url=http://blog.chron.com/ultimateastros/2014/09/16/george-springer-to-sit-rest-of-season/#22012101=0&26790103=0|work=[[Houston_Chronicle|Houston Chronicle]]|accessdate=September 16, 2014|date=September 16, 2014|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222223216/https://blog.chron.com/ultimateastros/2014/09/16/george-springer-to-sit-rest-of-season/#22012101=0&26790103=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他出賽78場，打擊率2成31，20轟51分打點，吞下114次三振。<ref name=wagner110217>{{cite newspaper |last=Wagner |first=James |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/11/02/sports/baseball/houston-astros-george-springer-mvp.html |title=Astros’ George Springer, the Series M.V.P., Has Come a Long Way |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=November 2, 2017 |accessdate=January 6, 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031630/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/11/02/sports/baseball/houston-astros-george-springer-mvp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2015年====
4月12日，史普林格在面對遊騎兵的比賽中，他於第10局接殺[[里昂尼斯·馬丁|里昂尼斯·馬丁]]可能擊出再見滿貫砲的飛球，最終太空人6比4贏球。

該年太空人靠著史普林格、[[荷西·奧圖維|荷西·奧圖維]]、[[卡洛斯·柯瑞亞|卡洛斯·柯瑞亞]]和[[達拉斯·凱戈|達拉斯·凱戈]]等球員，拿下美聯外卡。而他們先在外卡賽扳倒洋基，助球隊繼2005後再度闖入季後賽。不過太空人在分區賽2勝3敗不敵皇家，季後賽驚奇之旅很快就結束。
====2016年====
修正了自己的高三振率後，史普林格的成績逐漸進步，球隊也在該年讓他擔任比賽的開路先鋒。這年他162場比賽都沒有缺席，擊出29發全壘打，88次保送。不過球隊以84勝78敗排在美西第三，無緣季後賽。
====2017年====
該年球隊讓連續3年擔任右外野手的史普林格擔任中外野手。他在6月拿下個人首次單週最佳球員，野手首度入選明星賽。<ref name="USA Today Sports">{{cite newspaper |author=USA Today Sports |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2017/11/09/silver-slugger-awards-mlb/849087001/ |title=Jose Altuve, Nolan Arenado among repeat Silver Slugger Award winners |work=USA Today |date=November 9, 2017 |accessdate=November 10, 2017 |archive-date=2017-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115022851/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2017/11/09/silver-slugger-awards-mlb/849087001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年上半季，太空人就拿下60勝29敗，這也是隊史上半季最佳成績。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=https://www.mlb.com/astros/news/c-242006108 |title=Astros return from All-Star break on the heels of record-setting first half as top team in the league |work=MLB.com |date=July 13, 2017 |accessdate=January 24, 2018 |archive-date=2018-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125024153/https://www.mlb.com/astros/news/c-242006108 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月28日，他因為股四頭肌不適而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Boutwell|first1=Christian|title=George Springer placed on 10-day DL (quad injury)|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/244971706/george-springer-placed-on-disabled-list/|publisher=MLB|accessdate=July 28, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804003212/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/244971706/george-springer-placed-on-disabled-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他出賽140場比賽，打擊率2成83，34轟83分打點。這年，太空人以101勝61敗進入季後賽，並順利闖進世界大賽。最終太空人以4勝3敗打敗道奇，拿下隊史首冠。<ref>{{cite newspaper |last=Berg |first=Ted |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/06/sports-illustrated-houston-astros-2017-world-series-champs-mlb |title=Sports Illustrated cover declares Houston Astros '2017 World Series champs' |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] For the Win |date=June 25, 2014 |accessdate=November 2, 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124233106/https://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/06/sports-illustrated-houston-astros-2017-world-series-champs-mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>史普林格在第4場到第7場都有擊出全壘打，他在系列賽擊出11支安打，7分打點，<ref>{{cite news |last=Castrovince |first=Anthony |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/article/260386660/george-springer-named-world-series-mvp |title=Springer swats his way to MVP honors |work=MLB.com |date=November 2, 2017 |accessdate=November 2, 2017 |archive-date=2020-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200109222407/https://www.mlb.com/news/article/260386660/george-springer-named-world-series-mvp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=McTaggart |first1=Brian |last2=Gurnick |first2=Ken |title=Houston Astros win 2017 World Series |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/260380704/astros-beat-dodgers-to-win-first-world-series/ |work=MLB.com |date=November 2, 2017 |accessdate=November 2, 2017 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107012212/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/260380704/astros-beat-dodgers-to-win-first-world-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後拿下世界大賽MVP。

球季結束後，他拿下個人首座銀棒獎。
====2018年====
史普林格在該年成為史上首位連2年開幕戰都擊出首打席全壘打的選手。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/22958047/george-springer-houston-astros-hits-leadoff-home-run-opening-day-second-consecutive-season |title=Astros' George Springer hits leadoff HR for second straight Opening Day |first=Jerry |last=Crasnick |authorlink=Jerry Crasnick |date=March 30, 2018 |accessdate=March 30, 2018 |work=[[ESPN|ESPN]] |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129044718/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/22958047/george-springer-houston-astros-hits-leadoff-home-run-opening-day-second-consecutive-season |dead-url=no }}</ref>

5月7日，他成為隊史首位在9局內擊出6支安打的球員。1965年6月8日，Joe Morgan擊出6支安打，但是那場比賽打了12局。<ref>{{cite news |last=McTaggart |first=Brian |url=https://www.mlb.com/astros/news/george-springer-gets-6-hits-for-astros/c-275715936 |title=Springer's 6-hit night, 462-foot HR lead romp |work=MLB.com |language=en|date=May 7, 2018 |access-date=May 8, 2018}}</ref>

他與隊友[[艾力克斯·布萊格曼|艾力克斯·布萊格曼]]一同入選明星賽，並在延長賽擊出背靠背全壘打。<ref>{{citeweb |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/allstar/2018-allstar-game.shtml |publisher=Baseball Reference.com |title=2018 All-Star Game Box Score, July 17 |accessdate=October 12, 2018 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203102616/https://www.baseball-reference.com/allstar/2018-allstar-game.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月5日，他在滑壘時左手拇指受傷而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24302777/astros-outfielder-george-springer-dl-thumb-injury |title=Astros outfielder George Springer to DL with thumb injury |publisher=ESPN.com |date=August 6, 2018 |accessdate=October 13, 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031532/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24302777/astros-outfielder-george-springer-dl-thumb-injury |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他打擊率2成65，22轟71分打點。

2018年美聯分區賽第一場，史普林格擊出首打席全壘打，他也締造連續5場季後賽擊出全壘打的紀錄。最後球隊3場橫掃印地安人。史普林格在季後賽也累積10支全壘打，超越2004年由[[卡洛斯·貝爾川|卡洛斯·貝爾川]]締造的8支季後賽全壘打隊史紀錄。<ref>{{citeweb |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/george-springer-hits-2-alds-game-3-homers/c-297389204 |last=Footer |first=Alyson |title=George Springer hits 2 ALDS Game 3 homers |publisher=MLB.com |date=October 8, 2018 |accessdate=October 12, 2018 |archive-date=2019-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208104221/https://www.mlb.com/news/george-springer-hits-2-alds-game-3-homers/c-297389204 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2019年====
該年開幕戰，史普林格再一次擊出首打席全壘打。5月25日，他因為左腿筋緊繃而進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/nationals/springer-placed-on-10-day-il-with-left-hamstring-injury/2019/05/25/13b81d4c-7f24-11e9-b1f3-b233fe5811ef_story.html?noredirect=on|title=Springer place on 10-day IL with left hamstring injury|publisher=washingtonpost.com|date=May 25, 2019|accessdate=June 3, 2019}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

該年他的打擊率為2成92，39轟96分打點。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/springe01.shtml |title=George Springer Stats |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date= |accessdate=2019-10-11 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105061536/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/springe01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====2020年====
史普林格在這年的打擊率為2成65，並敲出14轟與32分打點。這年他挨了5次觸身球，為全大聯盟最多。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/springe01.shtml|title=George Springer Stats|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2019-10-13|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105061536/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/s/springe01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===多倫多藍鳥===
2021年1月20日，史普林格與藍鳥隊簽下6年1.5億美元的合約。

